div.div: Fig. 3. The heatmaps produced by this pipeline for segment 4. The total number of mutations in per every 100 nucleotides in the segment 4 reference genome is encoded by the heatmap for every sample strain. The pandemic strains are highlighted in red. In addition to being colored, the cells are annotated with the number of mutations too.
